name: Custom Leather Hip Bag by Go-Go
description: This bag screams, "look at me!!!!" We order these hip bags with the fringe design and decided to give a few custom looks to it. I guarantee you will NEVER see anyone else on with anything similar! This safety pin design was done by the owner of Go-Go Chic, one safety pin at a time. This kind of customization is not an easy or fast job.

name: Custom Denim Vest by Go-Go
description:
This vest went weak to CHIC! Karla boston, owner of Go-Go Chic once loved bleaching and cutting denim while in high school and now she's at it again! 
This vest was boring but now it is certainly a conversation piece. Customized with a new fab bleached design, rips, and a safety pin design on the front left collar and front right shoulder. 
This vest can be paired with almost any outfit. Sure to get plenty compliments in this custom Go-Go chic piece.
